  "instructions": [
    "Heat almond oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Stir in chili powder, turmeric, tomato paste, water, milk or almond milk, and canned tomatoes. Bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and let simmer for about 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Mix in green onions and shredded mozzarella cheese until melted and smooth.",
    "Stir in tagliatelle pasta and cook for an additional 5-7 minutes or until pasta is cooked through."
